company_role_research.user_prompt:
Company name: {company_name}
Website: {website}
Job role(s) open: {job_roles}
Recipient role: {recipient_role}

Do the following:
1) Describe what the company does in one simple sentence
2) Explain why companies at this stage usually hire this role
3) Identify one delivery or ownership pressure common at this stage
4) Explain what someone in this recipient's role likely worries about

email_1_conversation_starter.user_prompt:
Context:
Company: {company_name}
Hiring signal: {hiring_signal}
Recipient name: {recipient_name}
Recipient role: {recipient_role}
Industry: {industry}
Country: {country}

Write the first email as described in the rules.

persona_insights.user_prompt:
Build persona insights for:
Lead name: {lead_name}
Lead role: {lead_role}
Company: {company_name}
Company stage: {company_stage}
Background: {lead_background}

Provide:
1) Primary pain point for someone in this role
2) Key motivation/goal at this company stage
3) Current priority
4) Likely objection or concern
